title: TWO PRIVATE ROOFDECKS WITH CITY VIEWS
posting_body: ['TWO PRIVATE ROOFDECKS WITH CITY VIEWS', 'Listing ID #: 212995', 'Price: $3,899', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 1.0', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Balcony', 'City View', 'Dishwasher', 'Duplex', 'Hardwood', 'Light', 'Outdoor Space', 'Private Deck', 'Terrace', 'Soak in views of Manhattan and Queens directly from your own private terraces.', 'On the lower level you will find the updated kitchen with top of the line stainless steel appliances, white countertops, and ample cabinetry.', 'The kitchen opens up to your spacious living room with plenty of room for your furniture.', 'On the upper level of the duplex you will find the bedroom and full modern bathroom.', 'Private terrace on each level of the duplex.', 'Tons of natural light from every room!', 'Located just down the block from the subway on Astoria Blvd, coffee shop directly downstairs from the building, and plenty of restaurants, bars, shops for your convenience.', 'Contact Sofia at <URL> or 718-424-0813 to schedule your tour.', 'Sofia Aguirre', 'Phone: (718) 685-2775', 'Mobile: (718) 424-0813', 'Email: <URL>', 'The Bouklis Group \xa0 (718) 685-2775 \xa0 (718) 424-0813 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Sofia Aguirre at (718) 424-0813']
